    • Field Detail

      • ROTATION_DEADBAND

        public double ROTATION_DEADBAND
        The joystick z-axis value below which the robot will not rotate. this is to prevent accidental small twists of the joystick from affecting its trajectory.

      • MAX_ROTATION

        public static final double MAX_ROTATION
        The maximum speed that the robot is allowed to rotate at. The joystick value is scaled down to this value.
